data.title: A Time of Changes
data.meta_description: Garden City: Nelson Doubleday Inc., 1971. Book Club Edition. Hardcover. Near Fine in a Very Good jacket, generally toned and rubbed, some foxing throughout. Grey boards with black ink lettering on the spine, pushed at the head. Square and firmly bound, foxed at the top edge, clean internally. Silverberg's 1971 Nebula Award-winning novel. Near Fine / Very Good. Item #10231
